<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="24" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="23.[136,1458,843,2059]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,373,1751,1778]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Distribution:—</emphasis>
Trinidad, Guyana, Suriname, and Venezuela, Colombia, Peru and northern and west-central Brazil: Amazonas, Mato Grosso, Pará, Roraima. TDWG code: 81 TRT-OO 82 GUY-OO SUR-OO VEN-OO 83 CLM- OO PER-OO 84 BZC-MT BZN-AM BZN-PA BZN-RO.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="23.[136,1458,843,2059]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,484,1856,1883]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Diagnostic characters:—</emphasis>
